I am working on a regression problem and building a model using Random
Forest Regressor but while trying to get the accuracy I am getting
ValueError: continuous is not supported.



train=pd.read_csv(r"C:\Users\DELL\OneDrive\Documents\BigMart data\Train.csv")
test=pd.read_csv(r"C:\Users\DELL\OneDrive\Documents\BigMart data\Test.csv")
