The `main` method demonstrates how to use this `convertHoursToMinutes` method. It first declares an integer `hours` and sets its value to 5. It then calls `convertHoursToMinutes` method, passing `hours` as argument, and stores the returned value in the integer `minutes`. Finally, it prints the result.
