of quantum superposition on the comprehensive realm of quantum mechanics, and how it might shape the future path of quantum computing and quantum superposition? Could you also assess the potential consequences of quantum superposition on the broad scope of quantum mechanics, and how it might influence the future of quantum computing and quantum superposition?
