 the potential impacts of quantum superposition on the all-encompassing realm of quantum mechanics, and how it might shape the future direction of quantum informatics and quantum superposition? Could you also assess the potential repercussions of quantum superposition on the wide spectrum of quantum mechanics, and how it might influence the future of quantum informatics and quantum superposition?
