We will use Flask as our web framework due to its simplicity and flexibility. For the recommendation system, we will use Scikit-learn for building a content-based recommendation algorithm. We will use NLTK for text processing and TF-IDF for feature extraction. We will use SQLite as our database to store user preferences and reading habits. For the frontend, we will use Bootstrap to ensure a user-friendly and intuitive interface. We will also use the Flask-WTF library for creating the feedback form.

