I am using Slider Revolution on my website and I am using the Weglot plugin to translate the website to Arabic and Kurdish, but Weglot is not showing my slider images when I am translating the website to Kurdish and Arabic. I also added the media link to the translation but it is still not showing, it shows a white space.
