Sure, before we start creating the classifier, it's important to have the required libraries installed. You can do so using the pip package installer. We'll use "pandas" for handling our dataset, "numpy" for numeric operations, and "sklearn" for creating and evaluating the Decision Tree model.

Install them using the following command:
