To initiate the deployment of an Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2) virtual machine instance with advanced configuration settings, you can use an SDK like boto3 with Python. Here's an example on how to do it:

First, you need to make sure you have installed boto3 and AWS CLI then configure AWS CLI with the necessary API credentials.

```sh
pip install boto3
pip install awscli
