I am trying to add a logo to a sankey chart created using the code below but all attempts did not work:

library(networkD3)

p <- sankeyNetwork(Links = links, Nodes = nodes, Source = "IDsource", Target = "IDtarget", 
              Value = "value", NodeID = "name")
p


Any idea?
